    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Fili et Spiritu Sancti. Anni ab incarnatjone domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi millesimo sesagesimo quarto, pontificatus vero domni
                        nostri <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/265">Grecorius</persName> sumi
                        pontifitjs et universalis pape in apostolica sacratisima beati Petri
                        apostoli Domini sede ano primo, regnante domnus <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/77">Enricus</persName> res in Italia
                        ano detjmo, die octavo intrante mense agusto, indic(ione) duodetjma, in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Maiores #Minores
                            #Linen #Legumes #Houses #Casalia #Hay/fodder #Forests #Pigs #Levies #Rivers
                            #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters
                            #Land_clearing #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Venditio #Fluvial_transport #Plebs"
                            ref="#places/4181">Villa Martjana</placeName>. Petivi ad te quidem in
                        Dei nomine donnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4300"
                            >Ubertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abas</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monesterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Maiores #Minores
                            #Linen #Legumes #Poultry #Eggs #Houses #Casalia #Hay/fodder #Forests #Pigs #Levies #Rivers
                            #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters
                            #Land_clearing #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Venditio #Plebs #Fluvial_transport #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie qui vocatur in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Ponposia</placeName></orgName>, una per consensum
                        et auturitatem cunta regula monachorum deservientjum eiusdem monesterio
                        suprascripto patrone conceditore adque largitore, ut tibi presentem in Dei
                        nomine <persName><name ref="Rimbertus">Rimper</name>
                        </persName> qui est abitator in Villa Martjana tuisque filiis et heredibus,
                            <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellari nomine</rs> , concedo
                        adque largior seo confirmo tibi suprascripto petitore tuisque filis et
                        heredibus de rem iuris proprietatis monesterio nostro, idest tota omnes et
                        sortes et portjones quantascumque abeo per <rs key="#Venditio"
                            >conparatjonis</rs> et per cannbi lirtjaonis ad iure Sancte Marie qui
                        vocatur in Ponposia, ipsa suprascripta totam et integra res qui est posita
                        infra <rs key="#Comitatus">comitato </rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Maiores #Minores
                            #Linen #Legumes #Houses #Casalia #Hay/fodder #Forests #Pigs #Levies #Rivers
                            #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters
                            #Land_clearing #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Venditio #Plebs #Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/84">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Maiores #Minores
                                #Linen #Legumes #Houses #Casalia #Hay/fodder #Forests #Pigs #Levies #Rivers
                                #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters
                                #Land_clearing #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Venditio #Plebs #Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/80"> Ferrariense</placeName></geogName> et infra plebem
                            <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Maiores #Minores
                            #Linen #Legumes #Houses #Casalia #Hay/fodder #Forests #Pigs #Levies #Rivers
                            #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters
                            #Land_clearing #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Venditio #Plebs #Fluvial_transport"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1486">Sancti Stefani qui vocatur in Villa
                            Martjana</orgName>, per singula vel diversa locas, de omnia cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">teris</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pacuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">padulibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Rivers">aquis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscatjonibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venatjonibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Houses">casis</rs> seo et <rs key="#Casalia">casalibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">capellatjonibus</rs> ad
                        suprascripta totam ac integram res prelegitur. Hec omnia concedo adque
                        largior seo confirmo tibi suprascripto petitore tuisque filiis et heredibus
                        ad abendum, tenendum, posidendum, laborandum, cultandum, pastenandum,
                        suprasedendum, defensandum et in omnibus meliorandum in anis advenientibus
                        viginti et novem ad renovandum, salva caltjaria domnica dandum libellum
                        renovetur, sit iuste et ratjonabiliter a nobis petistis nec ab aliis minime
                        detinemur. Hoc est <rs key="#Levies">teratico</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs> in campo capa quarta, traendas ad
                        area, tritulatum per te petitore, <rs key="#Legumes">faba</rs> in area modio
                        quarto, <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">sicale</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">ordeo</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >fare</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals">mesturia ingranata</rs> in campo capa
                        quinta, traendas ad area et tritulatum per te petitore, <rs key="#Legumes"
                            >tjsercla</rs> seu <rs key="#Legumes">lenticula</rs> in area modio
                        quinto, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">trisico</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">mileo</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                            >panico</rs> in area modio sesto, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> mana detjma
                        gramulata, de <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> modio quarto, duabus vitjbus arbore
                        pecto ponentem et postea petitore cesum; et si vinea pastenaveritis extra
                        casale post in torta pervenerit, fruere debeatis amnis septe et postea
                        redere debeatis sicut de cetera vinea; et <rs key="#Land_clearing"
                            >ronco</rs> sit roncaveritis fruere debeatis amnis quinque et postea
                        rendere debeatis sicut de cetera tera et vale; si de sui <rs>graveritis</rs>
                        fruere debeatis amnis tres et postea rendere debeatis sicut de cetera tera;
                        et si portjo abueritis de ipsa <rs>silvagra</rs> fuerit de decem <rs
                            key="#Pigs">portj</rs> porco uno. Et concedo tibi in <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Fluvial_transport"
                            ref="#places/3597">Breuse</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">cascum tera</rs> qui e(st po *** Et insuper
                        concedo tibi de ipsa res quod est in lognitudinem sua perticas detjmpe[das]
                        ****************** et in latitudinem sua perticas detjmpedas **************
                        pro ipso casale <rs key="#Poultry">galina</rs> una et <rs key="#Eggs"
                            >oves</rs> quinque, ipsum teraticum domnicum per te petitore ubi <rs
                            key="#Fluvial_transport">navem nostra domnica</rs> potuerit
                        pervenire.</ab>
                </div>
